    <p><span>Mina the Hollower, Schrodinger's Call, Story of Seasons: Grand Bazaar, etc.</span>
      </p></div><div><p><em>007 First Light</em> for PlayStation 5, Xbox Series, and PC, and <em>Utawarerumono: Past and Present Rediscovered</em> for PlayStation 5, Switch 2, and PC are the highlights of this week’s Japanese video game releases. <span id="more-1049814"></span></p><p>Also due out this week are <em><a title="Games > Mina the Hollower [6 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/mina-the-hollower">Mina the Hollower</a></em> for <a title="Platforms > PS5 [11,514 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PlayStation 5</a>, <a title="Platforms > Xbox Series [8,796 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-series">Xbox Series</a>, <a title="Platforms > Switch 2 [1,049 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch-2">Switch 2</a>, <a title="Platforms > Switch [18,382 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch">Switch</a>, and <a title="Platforms > PC [25,613 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a>, <em><a title="Games > Schrodinger's Call [2 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/schrodingers-call">Schrodinger’s Call</a></em> for Switch and PC, and the PlayStation 5 and Xbox Series versions of&nbsp;<em><a title="Games > Story of Seasons: Grand Bazaar [13 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/story-of-seasons-grand-bazaar">Story of Seasons: Grand Bazaar</a></em>.</p><p>Get the full list of this week’s Japanese game releases below. It should be noted that <a title="Companies > Gematsu" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/gematsu">Gematsu</a> will receive a small percentage of money from purchases made through <a title="Companies > Playasia" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/playasia">Play-Asia</a> links. You can also save five percent with our multi-use “<strong>GEMATSU2025</strong>” coupon code.</p><h2><span>Physical and Digital</span></h2><ul><li><em><a title="Games > 007 First Light [12 articles]" href="https://ww