            <title><![CDATA[Brigandine: Abyss demo now available for PC]]></title>
            <link>https://www.gematsu.com/2026/05/brigandine-abyss-demo-now-available-for-pc</link>
            <guid>1529062</guid>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><div>

    <ul>
    <li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a></li>    </ul>

    
    <p><span>Try out the first two chapters of each story mode.</span>
      </p></div><div><p>A demo for fantasy war strategy RPG <em>Brigandine: Abyss</em> is now available for PC <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/3211430/BRIGANDINE_ABYSS/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Steam</a>, developer Happinet Corporation <a href="https://prtimes.jp/main/html/rd/p/000002693.000031422.html" target="_blank">announced</a>. PlayStation 5, Xbox Series, and Switch 2 versions will follow at a later date. <span id="more-1049800"></span></p><p>The demo features the first two chapters from both the “Gran Dragnica” and “Scarlet Will” story modes, allowing users to try out the early story, party formation, and combat. Save data from the demo cannot be transferred to the full release.</p><p><em><a title="Games > Brigandine: Abyss [2 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/brigandine-abyss">Brigandine: Abyss</a></em> is due out for <a title="Platforms > PC [25,613 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a> <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/3211430/BRIGANDINE_ABYSS/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Steam</a> on August 26, followed by PlayStation 5, Xbox Series, and Switch 2 and August 27.</p></div></div><br/><br/>https://www.gematsu.com/2026/05/brigandine-abyss-demo-now-available-for-pc]]></content:encoded>
            <dc:creator>invalid@example.com (ResetEra_Newsbot</dc:creator>
        </item>
