<!-- Moved from templates/posts/default.php -->

    <div><p>Bandai Namco has announced <em>Tekken 8</em> Season 3 downloadable content character Yujiro Hanma from the <em>Baki</em> series. He will launch in early 2027. <span id="more-1049793"></span></p><p><em><a title="Games > Tekken 8 [61 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/tekken-8">Tekken 8</a></em> is available now for <a title="Platforms > PS5 [11,514 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PlayStation 5</a>, <a title="Platforms > Xbox Series [8,796 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-series">Xbox Series</a>, and <a title="Platforms > PC [25,613 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a> via <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/1778820/TEKKEN_8/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Steam</a>.</p><p>Watch a teaser trailer below.</p><h2><span>DLC Character Yujiro Hanma Teaser Trailer</span></h2><p><strong>English</strong></p><p><iframe title="TEKKEN 8 – Yujiro Hanma Teaser" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/bvXW2ArNz7Q?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p><!-- AD: content -->
